        [
          "Staff Generated History"
        ],
        [
          "As a mortal you always knew you were the kinfolk of the murderous tribe of werewolves known as the Black Spiral Dancers.  Your family had long served them in San Diego and it was on a run for drugs and alcohol in Mexico that you were embraced by the Sabbat.  The Spiral Sign is your pack and it was your family connections that made the seer Xerxes seek you out. You and your pack are constantly searching for the right person, traits, rituals, or materials.  Most simply become regular vampires, others die in great agony.  None have turned into an Avatar of Caine yet, but it's only a matter of time.  You are a true believer in his prophecy that a Avatar of Caine will ascend the throne of Caine and as Regent of the Sabbat will lead the sect to victory against the Antediluveans.  Untill this great leader arises, it is hard for you to believe in all of the Sabbat's ideals."
        ],
